  "comment": "IGNITE180B LED Beam Moving Head: IGNITE180S LED SPOT Moving Head\nThe IGNITE180S is a powerful LED moving head with a 180W bright white LED source. Equipped with a double gobo wheel (with interchangeable gobos) to create stunning overlay effects. Combined with 2 individually rotating prisms (3+6) to make stunning aerial effects in 8 colours. The 15 degrees beam angle make this the ideal fixture to use for gobo projection and sharp beam figures.",
